Enactment of THE SEAWAY INTERNATIONAL BRIDGE CORPORATION, LTD. REGULATIONS
which provide that subsection 3(2) and sections 4, 9, 16, 17, 22, 24 and 25

shall apply, in a modified form, to this bridge company, effective
December 1, 1998.
